.TH PCAP_CLOSE 3PCAP "3 January 2014"
.SH NAME
pcap_close \- close a capture device or savefile
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.ft B
#include <pcap/pcap.h>
.ft
.LP
.ft B
void pcap_close(pcap_t *p);
.ft
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.BR pcap_close ()
closes the files associated with
.I p
and deallocates resources.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pcap (3PCAP)
